::Void::
"WildCat Alert WildCat Alert! The Cats Eye one has picked up a Astrotrain
Heading for space you know where he going."

::Liono::
Liono stand up and grabs the SparkReaver "Claws out cats." Liono open his 
chamber doors  sprints down the hallway towards the docking bay only to be 
cut off by Void.

::Void::
"Liono all the other Cats have put in this chip but you its field generator 
it generates scrambling field and detects cloaks fighters.Also my data tells 
me you fire Rockets were not as effective in space as they are on earth we 
made you this its only one piece of the suit but it all we have had time to 
test and finish." Void moves her arm forward as some repair and lab bots 
carry foward a low arm piece "It will increase your power in space and on 
earth."

::Liono::
Liono equips the piece as it locks on "Thanks I need to go Void you going to 
alright down here alone?" As Liono start moving again.

::Void::
"Sure nobody knows were cats layer is besides I doubt if they did they could 
reach it."

::Liono::
Liono reaches the port to see the Twin ships ready Liono gets in the Lion 
Assualt 2 to find Dark, Key ,Rinoa waiting and Tigerhawk waiting.
"Lets rock." Liono slides into helm with his normal amount of grace takes 
off. Liono looks at the view screen to see Hasimon taking off as well 
heading for outer Space.

::Koj::
"Liono this is Koj we are right behind you stay sharp. They have lead on us. 
Void gave power ups a few things on this trip that might be useful."
Koj takes the controls and levels the ship out before he prepares to exit 
the atmosphere
